        span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            br
            |  Well, since you’ve asked, here are a few. But note, even these are centered around our product, your idea doesn’t have to be:
        ul(style='margin-bottom:0cm;' type='disc')
        li(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            | A brand-new Application UX using ReactJS. Simple! Intuitive! Reactive! Flying slide-outs! Sliding fly-outs! All built in ReactJS!
        li(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            | VR course training! Think a How To guide you can interact with. How many YouTube videos does it usually take to find the perfect angle for that plumbing repair you need to do? In VR, you can look at the pipe from any angle right away.
        li(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            | Integration with collaboration tools. How about Just-in-time learning launched straight from Microsoft Teams? Or Fantasy Football for Dummies straight from a league page? Where else can learning be integrated so that it’s available with one click?
        li(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            | Conversation interfaces in our product. Maybe our users could press a “Help Me” button on any page and reach Customer Support! I’m not sure our Customer Support team would be thrilled with that button, but that’s the magic of an Ideathon – it’s just exploring possibilities.
        li(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            | And let’s not forget the biggest buzzword of our time – BLOCKCHAIN! Pretty much anything you can make using Blockchain technology will get instant bonus points (at least from me).
        p(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
