            br
            |  Nobody has asked any questions yet, but we’re guessing these are the questions people will most want to know.
        p(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
        em
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;') Can people work in teams?
        span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            br
            |  Yes! You can work individually or in teams up to 6 people.
        p(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
        em
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;') Why do we have to register?
        span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            br
            |  Just so that we can plan appropriately. If you forgot to register at the beginning, no problem. Go ahead and register as soon as you can.
        p(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
        em
            span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;') Does the result have to be shippable?
        span(style='font-size:14px;font-family:"Segoe UI",sans-serif;')
            br
            |  Not at all, however judges may give extra credit for submissions that more closely align with our products. But keep in mind that it may not always clear what ideas may be applicable to our product! Something that at first glance appears unrelated, for instance an app for a smart fridge, may actually grow to be a significant market differentiator (who hasn’t wanted to listen to an audio book while looking for a midnight snack!). This is primarily an opportunity to show off your ideas, not worry about how to market your solution.
        p(style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;')
